INSERT INTO post
(title, alias, description, content, publish_date, author_id, category_id, cover_id, status_id)
VALUES(
    'A Pirate''s Life is a love letter to the Pirates of the Caribbean films and the Disneyland attraction.',
    'a-pirates-life-is-a-love-letter-to-the-pirates-of-the-caribbean-films-and-the-disneyland-attraction',
    'A Pirate''s Life is a love letter to the Pirates of the Caribbean films and the Disneyland attraction.',
    '<p>Jack Sparrow, Davy Jones, and the world of Pirates of the Caribbean are set to collide with the world of <a href="/articles/sea-of-thieves-jack-sparrow-pirates-life-e3-2021">Sea of Thieves in the free A Pirate''s Life expansion on June 22,</a> and Rare has presented a showcase that dives deep into what makes this new adventure special for not only the players, but for the team who brought it to life.</p><h2>Yo Ho, Yo Ho, A Pirate''s Life for Me</h2><div class="jsx-2483022842 adunit-wrapper"><div id="5657232" class="jsx-2483022842 bobble bobble-0"><div class="jsx-2180275872"><div class="jsx-2180275872 slot-container blocked"><div id="slot-mediumAd-1631258687323" data-slot-info="{}" class="jsx-2180275872 slot-element"></div></div></div></div></div><p>The Pirates of the Caribbean-themed A Pirate''s Life expansion for <a href="/games/sea-of-thieves">Sea of Thieves</a> will arrive free to all players on June 22 and will bring with it five Tall Tales that will tell an original story the begins with players rescuing Jack Sparrow after he stole the "greatest pirate treasure of all time - a Golden Key to other lands." </p><output class="article-video-container"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-wrapper"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-container"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><div class="jsx-3424665568 player idle"><div class="jsx-3440876298 ad-wrapper hidden"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-3440876298 click-blocker hidden"><div class="jsx-3440876298 advertisement-label"></div><div class="jsx-3440876298 learn-more">Learn More</div></div><div class="jsx-3440876298 video-ad"><div class="jsx-3440876298 loading-container animation-default"><div class="jsx-3440876298 loading-now-playing animation-default">Now playing</div><div class="jsx-3440876298 loading-title animation-default">Sea of Thieves - A Pirate''s Life Reveal Trailer</div><div class="jsx-3440876298 loading-poster"><div class="jsx-3440876298 loading-anim animation-default"></div><div class="jsx-3440876298 loading-blur-anim animation-default"></div></div></div></div><div class="jsx-3440876298 ad-controls hidden"><div role="presentation" aria-label="play pause toggle" class="jsx-3440876298 play playing"></div><div class="jsx-402112792 volume-slider-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-402112792 volume-speaker low-volume muted"></div></div></div><div class="jsx-3440876298 ad-progress hidden"><div class="jsx-3440876298 current-progress" style="width: 0%; transition: width 350ms linear 0s;"></div>;</div></div><video playsinline="" preload="metadata" tabindex="0" crossorigin="anonymous" data-title="Sea of Thieves - A Pirate''s Life Reveal Trailer" thumbnail="https://assets1.ignimgs.com/thumbs/userUploaded/2021/6/13/sea-of-thieves-1623605042327.jpg" identifier="e83f16fc834cd24f1f601c13ae0d2d5a" live="false" class="jsx-1906181548 " src="blob:https://www.ign.com/069ff785-2d73-426d-b926-fc36e4b03b1b"></video><div class="jsx-578154794 video-overlay show-background"><div class="jsx-1855809287 video-header show"><a href="https://www.ign.com/videos/2021/06/13/sea-of-thieves-a-pirates-life-reveal-trailer" class="jsx-1855809287 title">Sea of Thieves - A Pirate''s Life Reveal Trailer</a></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 poster-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-2530077071 play"></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 duration">2:55</div><div role="presentation" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div><div role="presentation" hidden="" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></output><p>Jack Sparrow used this treasure to find the pirate world of Sea of Thieves, but he didn''t come alone. Davy Jones has also found his way in and quickly discovers he doesn''t have as much power in this new land as he does in his own. He has no dominion over the waves, and he doesn''t control the pirate''s life and their ability to return from the land of the dead. This obviously does not make him happy.</p><p>Throughout this story, players will work with Jack Sparrow as a member of their crew to stop Davy Jones and save the pirate''s life.</p><h2>Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Is a Love Letter to the Pirates of the Caribbean Films and Disneyland Attraction</h2><p>In creating this new expansion, Rare wanted to bring the best parts of both the Pirates of the Caribbean films and Disneyland attraction into the game. Besides the additions of Jack Sparrow and Davy Jones, players will also run into recreated scenes from the Pirates of the Carribbean ride, they will hear familiar music inspired by iconic songs from the films and attraction, and they will be able to customize their pirates and ships to make their Pirates of the Caribbean dreams come true.</p><p>There will be a ton of themed content for players to unlock, and it includes everything from being able to dress up like Jack Sparrow and the crew of the Black Pearl to having the prison dog with the keys as a pet on your ship to decking out your ship to honor the legend and legacy of the most famous pirate ships. </p><p>The team at Rare wanted this update to feel as authentic as possible, and to do so they even invited one of Jack Sparrow''s stunt doubles from the films in full make-up and costume to ensure A Pirate''s Life was as true to its source content as possible. </p><output class="widget-container"><div class="jsx-887634829 slideshow-preview"><div class="jsx-887634829 title">Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase</div><div class="jsx-887634829 images-container"><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-887634829 hero-image"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><img decoding="async" alt="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-10-pm-1623952797504.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=888" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image image jsx-219512600 expand" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-10-pm-1623952797504.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=888 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-10-pm-1623952797504.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=888&amp;dpr=2 2x"></div></div><div class="jsx-887634829 arrow-container"><div class="jsx-887634829 icon-wrapper"><svg class="ign-icon icon-right-arrow" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 18" aria-hidden="false" role="img" style="cursor: inherit; user-select: none; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: inline-block; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 3rem;"><title>Next</title><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" transform="translate(12.000000, 9.000000) rotate(180.000000) translate(-12.000000, -9.000000)" d="M9.00000004 1.00000003L1.00000007 9 9 16.99999993M22.99999954 9.00000016l-20.99999996 1e-8"></path></svg></div></div></button><div class="jsx-846688948 images-list"><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-887634829 gallery-image"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><img decoding="async" alt="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-11-pm-1623952797505.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image image jsx-219512600 expand" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-11-pm-1623952797505.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-11-pm-1623952797505.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9&amp;dpr=2 2x"></div></div><div class="jsx-887634829 image-count"><div class="jsx-887634829">29<!-- --> IMAGES</div></div></button><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-887634829 gallery-image"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><img decoding="async" alt="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-28-pm-1623952797505.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image image jsx-219512600 expand" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-28-pm-1623952797505.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-28-pm-1623952797505.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9&amp;dpr=2 2x"></div></div></button><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-887634829 gallery-image"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><img decoding="async" alt="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-30-pm-1623952797506.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image image jsx-219512600 expand" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-30-pm-1623952797506.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-30-pm-1623952797506.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9&amp;dpr=2 2x"></div></div></button><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-887634829 gallery-image"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><img decoding="async" alt="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-59-pm-1623952797507.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image image jsx-219512600 expand" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-59-pm-1623952797507.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-56-59-pm-1623952797507.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9&amp;dpr=2 2x"></div></div></button><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-887634829 gallery-image"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><img decoding="async" alt="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life Trailer — Xbox E3 2021 Extended Showcase" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-57-00-pm-1623952797507.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image image jsx-219512600 expand" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-57-00-pm-1623952797507.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2021/06/17/screen-shot-2021-06-17-at-1-57-00-pm-1623952797507.png?width=158&amp;crop=16%3A9&amp;dpr=2 2x"></div></div></button></div></div></div></output><h2>A Pirate''s Life Features Jack Sparrow as a Crew Member, New Enemies, New Locations, and Much More</h2><p>Jack Sparrow is much more than just another NPC, as he will be part of your crew and will help you in battle against Davy Jones'' ghost ships, Siren Statues, and more. Furthermore, he will be hanging around your ship and will tell you when your resources are low and will even allow you to take selfies with him.</p><p>A Pirate''s Life will also take players to brand new locations like the Sea of the Damned, Sailor''s Grave, and the Sunken Kingdom. An interesting note is that these new locations are linked to the main world by the Tunnels of the Damned. This area connects the game''s main world to the Sea of the Damned, allowing players to move where they need to go without impacting the main game negatively. Additionally, it also gives the team the possibility to "link the Sea of Thieves world with whatever we want."</p><p>One of these locations, the Sailor''s Grave, also features a tavern, gambling den, a ton of lore, and much more just waiting to be found, including a Easter Egg in the form of a ship that should make fans very happy. </p><p>Throughout the adventure, players will encounter new enemies like Sirens, Ocean Crawlers, and more. There are different types of these foes, and some will even attack you with electricity, poisonous spores, massive crab claws, or the Trident of Dark Tides.</p><p>Speaking of the Trident of Dark Tides, this new weapon blasts a powerful attack at enemies and can be found and used by the player in A Pirate''s Life and in the main Sea of Thieves adventure.</p><output class="article-video-container"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-wrapper"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-container"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><div class="jsx-3424665568 player idle"><div class="jsx-326516941 ad-wrapper hidden"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-326516941 click-blocker hidden"><div class="jsx-326516941 advertisement-label"></div><div class="jsx-326516941 learn-more">Learn More</div></div><div class="jsx-326516941 video-ad"><div class="jsx-326516941 loading-container animation-default"><div class="jsx-326516941 loading-now-playing animation-default">Now playing</div><div class="jsx-326516941 loading-title animation-default">Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life - Gameplay Trailer</div><div class="jsx-326516941 loading-poster"><div class="jsx-326516941 loading-anim animation-default"></div><div class="jsx-326516941 loading-blur-anim animation-default"></div></div></div></div><div class="jsx-326516941 ad-controls hidden"><div role="presentation" aria-label="play pause toggle" class="jsx-326516941 play playing"></div><div class="jsx-402112792 volume-slider-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-402112792 volume-speaker low-volume muted"></div></div></div><div class="jsx-326516941 ad-progress hidden"><div class="jsx-326516941 current-progress" style="width: 0%; transition: width 350ms linear 0s;"></div>;</div></div><video playsinline="" preload="metadata" tabindex="0" crossorigin="anonymous" data-title="Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life - Gameplay Trailer" thumbnail="https://assets1.ignimgs.com/thumbs/userUploaded/2021/6/17/sotslcinematicshot19-1623952834337.png" identifier="9e898842410e9d466c75d63c58cb8b29" live="false" class="jsx-1906181548 " src="blob:https://www.ign.com/8ccc4b8e-8d13-4af4-8071-b8264d647f24"></video><div class="jsx-1557704813 video-overlay show-background"><div class="jsx-1855809287 video-header show"><a href="https://www.ign.com/videos/2021/06/17/sea-of-thieves-a-pirates-life-gameplay-trailer" class="jsx-1855809287 title">Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life - Gameplay Trailer</a></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 poster-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-2530077071 play"></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 duration">1:43</div><div role="presentation" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div><div role="presentation" hidden="" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></output><h2>The First Two Tall Tales of A Pirate''s Life Explained</h2><p>In this showcase, Rare discussed a bit more of the first two Tall Tales in A Pirate''s Life, the first of which will have you searching for Jack Sparrow himself. Along the way, players will also find a Mysterious Castaway, who is the gatekeeper of these stories, and The Cursed Captain, a skull who you can carry around in your hand. Alongside helping you find Jack Sparrow, he will help you find secrets around Sailor''s Grave, comment on your dancing and sea shanties, and more.</p><p>The second Tall Tale will take you deep underwater, much further than ever before in Sea of Thieves, and will put you face-to-face with The Black Pearl and task you with finding Jack Sparrow''s compass. Unfortunately, it has been captured by the sirens and is chained to the bottom of the ocean. Players will also be able explore the Siren''s Citadel and interact with statues to raise and lower water levels to access new areas.</p><p>As previously mentioned, Sea of Thieves: A Pirate''s Life will be available free for all Sea of Thieves players on Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, and PC on June 22, 2021.</p>',
    '2021-06-20 10:51', 1, 1, ( SELECT id FROM post_cover WHERE filename = '02' LIMIT 1 ), 201);

