INSERT INTO post
(title, alias, description, content, publish_date, author_id, category_id, cover_id, status_id)
VALUES(
    'Battlefield 2042 Will Use AI Bots To Fill Multiplayer Matches, Allow Co-Op or Solo Play',
    'battlefield-2042-will-use-ai-bots-to-fill-multiplayer-matches-allow-co-op-or-solo-play',
    'Artificial intelligence will storm the battlefields for the first time in the series'' history.',
    '<p><a href="/games/battlefield-2042">Battlefield 2042</a> will fill the empty spots of 128-player matches with AI bots, allowing for full-player matches even if lobbies are not filled. These bots can also help facilitate playing Battlefield 2042 as a co-op or solo-player game. </p><div class="jsx-2483022842 adunit-wrapper"><div id="868781" class="jsx-2483022842 bobble bobble-0"><div class="jsx-2180275872"><div class="jsx-2180275872 slot-container blocked"><div id="slot-mediumAd-1631260371685" data-slot-info="{}" class="jsx-2180275872 slot-element"></div></div></div></div></div><p>As revealed in an update to the <a target="_blank" href="https://answers.ea.com/t5/Battlefield-Announcements/Battlefield-Briefing-Welcome-to-2042/m-p/10415599?utm_campaign=bf2042_hd_ww_ic_soco_twt_tw-battlefield-briefing&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;cid=69004&amp;ts=1623780406111#M1" rel="noopener noreferrer">Battlefield Briefing EA Answers page</a>, AI Soldiers is a new bot system being added to Battlefield 2042. "Also new is the introduction of AI Soldiers (Artificial Intelligence) to the series," the post reads. "As a multiplayer-only experience, it’s important for us to let you play Battlefield 2042 when and how you want."</p><output class="article-video-container"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-wrapper"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-container"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><div class="jsx-3424665568 player idle"><div class="jsx-3064873951 ad-wrapper hidden"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-3064873951 click-blocker hidden"><div class="jsx-3064873951 advertisement-label"></div><div class="jsx-3064873951 learn-more">Learn More</div></div><div class="jsx-3064873951 video-ad"><div class="jsx-3064873951 loading-container animation-default"><div class="jsx-3064873951 loading-now-playing animation-default">Now playing</div><div class="jsx-3064873951 loading-title animation-default">Battlefield 2042 - Reveal Trailer</div><div class="jsx-3064873951 loading-poster"><div class="jsx-3064873951 loading-anim animation-default"></div><div class="jsx-3064873951 loading-blur-anim animation-default"></div></div></div></div><div class="jsx-3064873951 ad-controls hidden"><div role="presentation" aria-label="play pause toggle" class="jsx-3064873951 play playing"></div><div class="jsx-402112792 volume-slider-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-402112792 volume-speaker low-volume muted"></div></div></div><div class="jsx-3064873951 ad-progress hidden"><div class="jsx-3064873951 current-progress" style="width: 0%; transition: width 350ms linear 0s;"></div>;</div></div><video playsinline="" preload="metadata" tabindex="0" crossorigin="anonymous" data-title="Battlefield 2042 - Reveal Trailer" thumbnail="https://assets1.ignimgs.com/thumbs/userUploaded/2021/6/9/bf-2042-screenshot-map-vista-borderlinejpgadaptcrop16x9818p-1-1623253717954.jpg" identifier="803d54da458ac0e62f1c206848f08be7" live="false" class="jsx-1906181548 " src="blob:https://www.ign.com/97110ca3-677e-4e40-8944-1cf3d599714c"></video><div class="jsx-4265115007 video-overlay show-background"><div class="jsx-1855809287 video-header show"><a href="https://www.ign.com/videos/2021/06/09/battlefield-2042-reveal-trailer" class="jsx-1855809287 title">Battlefield 2042 - Reveal Trailer</a></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 poster-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-2530077071 play"></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 duration">4:59</div><div role="presentation" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div><div role="presentation" hidden="" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></output><p>AI Soldiers will ensure matches are filled with 128 players, but they are used for other purposes, too. Despite being a multiplayer game, these bots also help transform Battlefield 2042 into a co-op or single-player game. </p><p>In Conquest and Breakthrough modes, players can opt for a co-op experience that "allows you to play together with friends, against AI soldiers," or even a solo version for those playing alone. "If you wish to perfect your skills for multiplayer, you can even play alone against AI soldiers," reveals the blog.</p><p></p><p>Before Battlefield 2: Modern Combat launched on PlayStation 2 and Xbox, Battlefield games were exclusively multiplayer and did not have campaigns. As such, if you wanted to play the likes of Battlefield 1942 or Battlefield Vietnam without other real players, you were completely stumped. Battlefield 2042 marks a milestone in the series history; an option to finally experience its wild-scale combat without having to play with others.  </p><p>For more on Battlefield 2042, check out the <a href="/videos/battlefield-2042-desert-storm-gameplay-trailer">explosive gameplay trailer from E3 2021</a>, our <a href="/articles/battlefield-2042-first-look-preview-man-vs-man-vs-nature">first-look preview</a>, and the news that it <a href="/articles/battlefield-2042-no-campaign-battle-royale-mode">won''t have a battle royale mode</a>. </p><div class="divider-container"><hr class="accent-divider"></div><p><em>Matt Purslow is IGN''s UK News and Entertainment Writer. </em></p>',
    '2021-06-16 18:12', 5, 1, ( SELECT id FROM post_cover WHERE filename = '08' LIMIT 1 ), 201);

--

