INSERT INTO post
(title, alias, description, content, publish_date, author_id, category_id, cover_id, status_id)
VALUES(
    'E3 Awards 2021: Forza Horizon 5 is the Most Anticipated Game of the Show',
    'e3-awards-2021-forza-horizon-5-is-the-most-anticipated-game-of-the-show',
    'Halo: Infinite and Tiny Tina''s Wonderlands also among the games highlighted.',
    '<p>Halo: Infinite, Mario + Rabbids: Sparks of Hope, and <a href="/games/forza-horizon-5">Forza Horizon 5</a> were some of the winners in <a href="/articles/e3-2021-schedule-date-events-games-news">E3 2021</a>. They were all among the most anticipated games selected during today''s <a href="/articles/e3-2021-awards-show">E3 2021 Awards Show</a>, which were selected by the editors at IGN, GameSpot, PC Gamer, and GamesRadar+.</p><div class="jsx-2483022842 adunit-wrapper"><div id="3638226" class="jsx-2483022842 bobble bobble-0"><div class="jsx-2180275872"><div class="jsx-2180275872 slot-container blocked"><div id="slot-mediumAd-1631260652734" data-slot-info="{}" class="jsx-2180275872 slot-element"></div></div></div></div></div><output class="article-video-container"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-wrapper"><div class="jsx-283099997 jsx-2147466702 video-container"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-container aspect-ratio-16-9"><div class="jsx-3905315446 aspect-ratio-child"><div class="jsx-3424665568 player idle"><div class="jsx-2061793999 ad-wrapper hidden"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-2061793999 click-blocker hidden"><div class="jsx-2061793999 advertisement-label"></div><div class="jsx-2061793999 learn-more">Learn More</div></div><div class="jsx-2061793999 video-ad"><div class="jsx-2061793999 loading-container animation-default"><div class="jsx-2061793999 loading-now-playing animation-default">Now playing</div><div class="jsx-2061793999 loading-title animation-default">Forza Horizon 5 - Release Date Trailer</div><div class="jsx-2061793999 loading-poster"><div class="jsx-2061793999 loading-anim animation-default"></div><div class="jsx-2061793999 loading-blur-anim animation-default"></div></div></div></div><div class="jsx-2061793999 ad-controls hidden"><div role="presentation" aria-label="play pause toggle" class="jsx-2061793999 play playing"></div><div class="jsx-402112792 volume-slider-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-402112792 volume-speaker low-volume muted"></div></div></div><div class="jsx-2061793999 ad-progress hidden"><div class="jsx-2061793999 current-progress" style="width: 0%; transition: width 350ms linear 0s;"></div>;</div></div><video playsinline="" preload="metadata" tabindex="0" crossorigin="anonymous" data-title="Forza Horizon 5 - Release Date Trailer" thumbnail="https://assets1.ignimgs.com/thumbs/userUploaded/2021/6/13/forza-1623607964992.jpg" identifier="416a88db32c77552511db1a60cdd173b" live="false" class="jsx-1906181548 " src="blob:https://www.ign.com/d3fe697c-9b21-4142-94c6-7ef91fbb51d9"></video><div class="jsx-3209639503 video-overlay show-background"><div class="jsx-1855809287 video-header show"><a href="https://www.ign.com/videos/2021/06/13/forza-horizon-5-release-date-trailer" class="jsx-1855809287 title">Forza Horizon 5 - Release Date Trailer</a></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 poster-container"><div role="presentation" class="jsx-2530077071 play"></div><div class="jsx-2530077071 duration">1:55</div><div role="presentation" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div><div role="presentation" hidden="" class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-container"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-message"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-toggle"><div class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-icon on"></div></div><span class="jsx-1965293124 autoplay-text"><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-left">Autoplay setting: </span><span class="jsx-1965293124 text-right">On</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></output><p>With E3 2021 mostly behind us, we were able to pick some of the most exciting games shown throughout the show. Here''s the full list of awards, which were presented during the E3 live broadcast. </p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Ubisoft Most Anticipated Game:</strong> Mario + Rabbids: Sparks of Hope</li><li><strong>Gearbox Most Anticipated Game: </strong>Tiny Tina''s Wonderlands</li><li><strong>Xbox/Bethesda Most Anticipated Game:</strong> Halo: Infinite</li><li><strong>Square Enix Most Anticipated Game: </strong>Marvel''s Guardians of the Galaxy</li><li><strong>PC Gaming Show Most Anticipated Game:</strong> Songs of Conquest</li><li><strong>Future Games Show Most Anticipated Game: </strong>Immortality</li><li><strong>Intellivision Most Anticipated Game: </strong>Dolphin Quest</li><li><strong>Mythical Games Most Anticipated Game: </strong></li><li><strong>Most Anticipated Indie Game:</strong> Falling Frontier</li><li><strong>Freedom Games Most Anticipated Game:</strong> Airborne Kingdom</li><li><strong>Capcom Most Anticipated Game:</strong> The Great Ace Attorney Chronicles</li></ul><ul><li><strong>Nintendo Most Anticipated Game: </strong>Breath of the Wild 2</li><li><strong>Most Anticipated Yooreka Studio Game:</strong> Loopmancer</li></ul><ul><li><strong>Best Presentation: </strong>Xbox and Bethesda Showcase</li><li><strong>Most Anticipated Game Overall: </strong>Forza Horizon 5</li></ul><p></p><p></p><p>The E3 Awards Show was presented by Greg Miller, Jacki Jing, and Alex Mendez. It capped off a week of showcase events for the games industry featuring Starfield, Far Cry 6, and other anticipated games.</p><p>But while the main part of E3 2021 is finished, the <a href="/articles/summer-of-gaming-2021-schedule-how-to-watch-announcements-games-date-time">Summer of Gaming</a> rolls on. On Thursday, Microsoft will be hosting the <a href="/articles/xbox-games-showcase-extended-announced-for-thursday-double-fine-obsidian-ninja-theory-rare">Xbox Games Showcase: Extended</a>, which will feature even more announcements. </p><p>In the meantime, check out all of our coverage of Forza Horizon 5, including our extensive <a href="/articles/in-depth-with-forza-horizon-5-the-largest-most-diverse-horizon-ever">Forza Horizon 5 preview and interview</a>.</p>',
    '2021-06-15 04:58', 6, 1, ( SELECT id FROM post_cover WHERE filename = '09' LIMIT 1 ), 201);

